257
00:19:39,800 --> 00:19:42,490
Yeah... I know.

258
00:19:42,490 --> 00:19:43,190
--Serious Power!

259
00:19:43,190 --> 00:19:44,950
--Whoa, amazing, amazing...
--Serious Power!

260
00:19:45,970 --> 00:19:49,200
Wait! If you're willing to
go that far to get there...

261
00:19:51,240 --> 00:19:53,150
...there's a ropeway to the castle.

262
00:19:53,150 --> 00:19:57,380
Can't be. There's no rope
connected to the castle any more.

263
00:19:57,880 --> 00:20:02,010
There's one. Someone has
reattached a white rope...

264
00:20:02,010 --> 00:20:04,890
...from a big tree at the
edge of Gyasta to the castle!

265
00:20:05,710 --> 00:20:06,980
Gyasta?

266
00:20:06,980 --> 00:20:10,460
That's the name of the town
that Dr. Kureha headed last.

267
00:20:11,410 --> 00:20:12,870
Hey, Luffy!

268
00:20:13,230 --> 00:20:13,890
Huh?

269
00:20:13,890 --> 00:20:14,990
Where is that guy?

270
00:20:14,990 --> 00:20:15,850
That guy?

271
00:20:16,690 --> 00:20:17,990
He's not here!

272
00:20:17,990 --> 00:20:18,930
Which guy?

273
00:20:18,930 --> 00:20:21,230
That tin bastard! He's disappeared!

274
00:20:21,230 --> 00:20:22,650
Ahhh! Ahhh! Ahhh!

275
00:20:25,860 --> 00:20:30,250
He came up on the haired hippo.
He wouldn't go down on his own.

276
00:20:30,580 --> 00:20:32,840
When on earth did he...

277
00:20:32,840 --> 00:20:35,880
While you were fascinated by
the transformations, of course!

278
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:40,840
That bastard! I'll find him
right away and finish him off!

279
00:20:41,510 --> 00:20:44,040
Don't tell me he got into
the castle from somewhere...

280
00:20:44,760 --> 00:20:46,300
If that's the case, Nami-san will be...

281
00:20:48,390 --> 00:20:50,830
That bastard! If he lays
his hands on Nami-san,

282
00:20:50,830 --> 00:20:52,310
--Hold it!
--I'll gut him 100 times!

283
00:20:53,460 --> 00:20:57,270
Geez, does he want to die?

284
00:20:57,570 --> 00:20:58,910
Doctorine...

285
00:20:58,910 --> 00:20:59,720
Hmm?

286
00:21:00,980 --> 00:21:03,240
He called me...

287
00:21:06,420 --> 00:21:08,120
his friend...

288
00:21:18,660 --> 00:21:22,460
Where're you, annoying mouth?!

289
00:21:23,590 --> 00:21:26,090
Seems like my fever is
coming down quite a bit.

290
00:21:26,630 --> 00:21:30,250
At this rate, it's likely that
I can go back to the ship soon.

291
00:21:32,470 --> 00:21:34,410
What am I doing?!

292
00:21:34,900 --> 00:21:39,160
This is no time to be in bed resting here!
Vivi is waiting for me!

293
00:21:43,050 --> 00:21:46,000
What the heck is going on here?!

294
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:48,570
Is this really my Drum Castle?

295
00:21:50,360 --> 00:21:53,290
What have they done to my castle?

296
00:21:55,200 --> 00:21:57,910
They won't get away with this!

297
00:21:58,980 --> 00:22:02,460
I will chew up every single one of them!

298
00:22:15,390 --> 00:22:24,170
Even this sleepless town
has dozed off for now

299
00:22:25,690 --> 00:22:36,830
From today forth,
something's going to change

300
00:22:36,830 --> 00:22:46,620
I'm sure I can start fresh,
since I'm not alone

301
00:22:47,090 --> 00:22:57,290
Just by having you by my side,
I feel I can become strong

302
00:22:57,560 --> 00:23:08,030
I wonder how far I can go,
towards the place that leads to the future

303
00:23:08,030 --> 00:23:16,380
Off in the distance it shines,
encompassing the world

304
00:23:16,380 --> 00:23:20,040
Before dawn

305
00:23:25,250 --> 00:23:28,040
I should get out of here quickly
while Doctorine isn't around!

306
00:23:28,040 --> 00:23:31,010
That bastard! I'll find him
right away and finish him off!

307
00:23:31,010 --> 00:23:33,760
If he lays his hands on Nami-san,
I'll gut him 100 times!

308
00:23:33,760 --> 00:23:35,630
Oh no! He looks like a bad guy!

309
00:23:35,630 --> 00:23:37,400
I've cornered you, annoying mouth!

310
00:23:37,400 --> 00:23:38,890
Dalton-san's got dynamites!

311
00:23:38,890 --> 00:23:41,270
I have no idea what's going on here.

312
00:23:41,270 --> 00:23:42,600
On the next episode of One Piece!

313
00:23:42,600 --> 00:23:46,400
"When The Kingdom's Rule Ends!
